<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="fight-v">fight <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /faɪt/    美 /faɪt/  </p>
<p>(fought,fought)vi &amp; vt</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(与…) 作战；打 (仗)；(与……) 战斗：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He died <strong>fighting for</strong> his country. 
他为国阵亡。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In World War <strong>Ⅱ</strong> , England <strong>fought</strong> with France <strong>against</strong> Germany.
第二次世界大战中，英国和法国联合与德国作战。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>For many parents, raising a teenager is like fighting a long war.
对许多父母来说，养一个十几岁的孩子就像打一场持久战。</p><footer>2010 湖北</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(与…) 打斗；(与…) 打架；(与……) 争吵：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The boys are fighting.
男孩子们在打架。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She fought him desperately, kicking and biting.
她又踢又咬，与他拼命厮打。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They are always <strong>fighting about / over</strong> money.
他们总是为钱吵架。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>努力争取；(为…) 奋斗：</strong></h4>
<p>to try hard to do or get sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I felt as if I had reached the goal that I had been <strong>fighting for</strong>.
我感觉似乎达到了自己一直为之所奋斗的目标。</p><footer>人教新必修① – 5</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I had to stay in hospital for weeks while the doctors <strong>fought to</strong> save my life.
我只好住院几周，在这期间医生奋力挽救我的生命。</p><footer>2013 四川</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The Chinese women's volleyball team has <strong>fought</strong> their <strong>way</strong> through ups and downs.
中国女排一路拼搏，经历了起起落落。</p><footer>外研新选必① – 3</footer></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>抵抗；克制；(与…) 斗争：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When you feel like crying, don't fight it.
想哭的时候就哭出来吧，别忍着。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>fight poverty / cancer</strong>
与贫穷/癌症抗争</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="fight-back">fight back</h3>
<p>1.<strong>反击；回击；克制：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Lewis fought back to win the game.
刘易斯奋起反击，以赢得比赛。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She looked away, fighting back her tears.
她看着别处，强忍着泪。</p></div></div>